    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2010 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) represents the pinnacle of hydraulic-steering precision and naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies a 3.8L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), outputting 385 hp through a rare and engaging 6-speed manual transaxle. This example is in concours-level condition, featuring an immaculate undercarriage, original paint with deep luster, and a factory-spec interior. Performance is bolstered by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono Package Plus, ensuring optimal damping and throttle response. With a documented service history and zero mechanical flaws, this is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
